column3: “This got me so high that I was convinced that the street light outside my house was the moon. Luckily my friend pointed out that that's no moon"”"
“IT TRIPS U THE FUCK OUT”
“One of my all time favorite strains hands down. Awesome high but not overwhelming in proper doses.”

“very good taste, not once was it a harsh smoke. Very trippy high (couple mild hallucinations) and afterwards, the uncontrolable laughs. honestly it's without a doubt the best grass i've ever smoked.”

“With three hits from this it tastes woodsy with tea herbs. Very Euphoric and keeps my mind entertained by getting my tasks done.  This is rather unusual warm numbing sensation, although duly noted not to take over 205º C, if you want a smoother smoke. I was feeling a bit bored and sleepy  way to early to go to sleep. I've Had Master Kush and skywalker separate and they are both really great hitters. I'm Doing Master ...”

“Wicked good Kush, Very strong taste, matches the buzz. Strong.
Great body high that lasts so very long, great with anxiety, nervousness, etc. Long time patient recommends. Highly.”

“This strain has very dense nugs and populated with just the right amount of orange hairs and crystals. Me and a couple buddies smoked 26 blunts of this strain and let me tell you something, we were fucking stoned. The weed gods picked us up by their Hands and took us to nugopolis. Our legs were tingly and numb. I would drift into space for a while and come back for a second. Being in the dark while high off this stra...”
“Man what can I say. You can feel the force And that's awesome. One of the best strains out their don't let the force pass you by”
“Man what can I say. You can feel the force And that's awesome. One of the best strains out their don't let the force pass you by”
“Relaxing high, buds are a bit stringy and has a soap taste probably won't buy it again”

“I don't know the exact name of this strain but i can definitely feel the force in this one. I has this sort of tingly sensation all over my body. Not so much on the head which is a plus for me. But if you are looking for something to relax to, i'd go with the jedi.”
“Nice Jedi is.”

“ABSOULOUTLY  Feel in love with Master Jedi , It smoked very good to the point I need another hit . No chocking none of that , and I can say it made me pretty creative ... Master Jedi You are the MASTER !”

“Good Shit! Smells like you woluld expect from a Master Kush x Jedi. Has the Piney scent from the Master and kind of fruity from the Jedi. Great smoke, gets you moderately stoned with good head and body effects. Won't knock you out but will make you lazy.  Just feels nice & mellow. Good indica for later on in the day.”
“Always Fresh Master Jedi.  It takes away the pain so that I can have energy to do chores or just set and watch a good movie.  It does not make you paranoid.  Nice and smooth no chocking.”
“Very strong strain, got me high and put me to sleep pretty fast!”
“Always Fresh Master Jedi.  It takes away the pain so that I can have energy to do chores or just set and watch a good movie.  It does not make you paranoid.  Nice and smooth no chocking.”
“Great strain!!! Nice body high and excellent relaxation!!! Felt very uplifted/euphoric and also noticed I was able to hold long conversations.”
“much like you Ky-lo Ren this strain is lost and confused. No distinct taste, burned my throat a little while smoking it. Wish the high were stronger”
“Definitely felt the force tingle through me once or twice 😉”

“ABSOULOUTLY  Feel in love with Master Jedi , It smoked very good to the point I need another hit . No chocking none of that , and I can say it made me pretty creative ... Master Jedi You are the MASTER !”

“HELLO leafly community I AM THE BREEDER OF MASTER JEDI !!! The  Reason I called it MASTER JEDI is because this is the Original
 Jedi 41 X JEdi 41= MASTER JEDI   
These seeded were purchased from a guy that showed me his reciept for these expensive rare strain. It is extremely great medical marijuana ! Awesome body high, very potent indica. I traced genetics and it said that Jedi 41 = LIONS HEAD X WHITE RHINO !!!! Whi...”
“Nice Jedi is.”

“I don't know the exact name of this strain but i can definitely feel the force in this one. I has this sort of tingly sensation all over my body. Not so much on the head which is a plus for me. But if you are looking for something to relax to, i'd go with the jedi.”
“Great strain!!! Nice body high and excellent relaxation!!! Felt very uplifted/euphoric and also noticed I was able to hold long conversations.”
“This is one of my top 2 strains. I hit it and it triangles all  the way down to my toes :)”
“Definitely felt the force tingle through me once or twice 😉”

“wow! so I just paid 3k in taxes, then had a root canal with two fillings. I opted to get this instead of pain pills from the dentist. as soon as I smoked the pain in my jaw was gone. the high from the dentist was gone as well, and I felt totally fine, clear headed, and happy. this is an indica winner!”

“10/10 🤚👁️ feeling one with the force 
67% chance you'll feel like you're a bad ass master starlord.
☑️ Check if yo daddy evil”
“This is an incredibly stoney strain. My pain is relieved almost instantly!”
“Pretty good high in general, got so hungry I spent $67 on Arby’s but hey I can’t complain.”

“Haven't had this in a long time. But it was one of my favorites. The smell is incredibly dank. Fills up a building. Nothing else smells like it. Very unique. For description purposes, I was told the genetics were Hindu Kush and GDP. Also goes by Master Jager.”

“Definitely one of the best Star Wars strains that I have had... The effects are strong and kick in almost as soon as you exhale. Nice dense, dank and frosty buds. Perfect strain for a rainy day at home; a nice and relaxing/euphoric high, but also very Stoney (I haven’t felt stoned like this since high school!) If you come across this strain BUY IT! I promise you won’t be disappointed...”
“awesome strain”

“Great for relieving stress and concentration. Smoked a jay after a very stressful long week and one joint between 5x people was enough to make us all feel uplifted and stress free. Also great for sleep, a bowl before bed had me sleeping soft and soundly. The force is strong with this strand.”
“Favorite Strain & not just because I like Star Wars! It doesn't make me paranoid like it says it can. This was the 1st strain I tried & I've tried many.”
“Its pretty dank”
“I definitely felt the force in this one!! Im so stoned! Hahahaha!!! xD”
“Vaped, smoked or eaten this strain works wonderfully for my needs.”
“So stinky! Potent fruity almost purpley flavor. Very good smoke, a little more harsh than I thought but it sure does a number late at night! Top 3 strains for me!”
“This strain is a great nighttime smoke. Both the bud and dank smell amazing. This strain doesn't knock me out like some other indicts but is definitely relaxing. I would buy again.”

“Kushy flavor with a slight taste of citrus on the exhale.
Very sedative, couch-locky strain. Good for sleep.”

“Very good strain for nighttime users. Subjects will notice
 Very uplifting head high. The user will feel dialed in" mentally. Body effects are minimal

“VERY GOOD SMOKE
open the bag and the room fills with lemony goodness
relieved the pains and increased appetite was 
a very pleasant experience”
“My favorite strain!!! Now I have an MMJ strain to go along with my love of Stars Wars! It also doesn't make me paranoid like it says it can. That's always plus!”

“If you have had a long day and need to relax, this is the strain for you. Spent a good hour or two stoned in bed laughing my ass off at my favourite show. The musky smell is amazing but can be overbearing if you don't want to be noticed. Definitely an amazing strain.”
“Great strain severe couch lock but in a good way sweet exhale taste really nice the force is strong with this one " oh yeah I went there”"

“Picked this one up for real cheap. It was a nice surprise with large heavy buds packed with keef. I liked the body relaxing sensation and the clear headedness of it. Not too couch lock for an indica which is always welcome. Highly recommend, will take some pain and depression away”

“My experience with this particular strain was mostly great. Nugs were a bit brighter than the usual kush colors. The scent was somewhat a mixture of pine, sweetness, and quite pungent. I have experience with one of the parents of this strain, that being Master Kush. And in a way it is very similar to that strain. The onset of the high comes on slower than most indicas. Your body will start to feel more relaxed as the...”
“Really enjoyed this strain! I felt like I could work and have fun doing it”
“This strike. Is #1 for my needs!”
“awesome strain cant go wrong heavy buzz”
“the force is definitely strong with this strain..great feeling outdoor. .sun was shining brighter ..overall euphoria”

“Picked this up along with a few other Indicas and Indica dominant hybrids.  By comparison, this was not as potent overall, and definitely more head than body which surprised me for an Indica.  Also found this an especially harsh vape.  High was decent and enjoyable, but not what I look for in a good Indica.”
“very light head high. i was able to focus on housework and homework. didnt last very long but deff my new buddy for the wake n bake before work”
“Made me feel relaxed and definitely took my mind off things.”
“Good stuff!!”

“I smoked one moderately sized bowl (0.3g) out of a clean hand pipe. Great earthy flavors with citrus and sweet after taste exactly as the description states. Generally I do not cough but this one made me cough on the first few pulls. The herb was on the drier side. Over the first fifteen minutes I began to feel an extreme head high yet a strong state of focus and energy. In the next half an hour I experienced intense...”

“Received a fresh batch from local care-giver and the buds that I had were covered in crystals and a tons of burnt orange hairs.  Very visually appealing and definitely passed the eye test.  High was relaxing but not overwhelming.  Could see this as a daytime bud (with small doses) but also a nice chill out at end of the day buzz with a bit more.  Would not hesitate to purchase again!”

“Picked some of this up from my dispensary recently. My sample seems to be super potent and gives me a very intense experience. It's more head high than I was expecting and has strong body effects as well. I find it to last a long time. The first hour or so being intense, then gradually transitioning to a very nice relaxing high. It keeps me up for a good hour plus after I smoke it so I keep that in mind when smoking ...”
“GG”

“So I got an 1/8 of this today. Reviews had me hyped on it. Loaded a nice vape bowl. Took 3 big hits. I loved the taste of this!! Tasted so much lighter than it smelled.  Really tasty. Sweet, piney and citrusy to me.   After about 15 mins I got kinda shakey feeling and that's now transpired into a warm buzzy feeling in my body. I feel kinda spaced out and relaxed and much more in my head than the OG 18.  Still not su...”
“Head high was stronger than the body high. It was okay for RLS, but gave me really disturbing dreams. Very relaxing for muscles, so much so that I kept feeling like I had to poop!! Not cool.”
“Excellent flower if you catch it when it's nice and plump. Get a big big of this one because you will crumble it down till it's all gone”
